item.title: Sigs i have made
item.dc:creator: @_rezzy »rezzy.
item.description:
@_rezzy wrote:

WTF is this…
Man get better ways than just getting focals and adding stupid renders.
Your renders suck, and your renders suck.
Your sources might suck, but I bet even if you had good sources, you’d still fuck it up.
Do you know why? Well, for one of your Halo ones, I made one with the stock as well and it didn’t look stretched. What you did is took the stock and resized the whole fucking thing without aspect, you just squished the shit out of it, same thing with your renders. Your renders don’t have to take the whole height and or width.
I can make a better one effortlessly, if you want to see, someone reply to this and say so.
I’ll make one with not much effects, mostly a stock and added stupid stuff and that’s it.
if you want me to make a serious one (I suck.) just say so and I will.
But seriously, even my first tags didn’t look this fucking horrid.
[center] It could’ve been said a nicer way.[/center]
